{
    "story_id": "",
    "story_name": "爱如流星 守护家人的方法",
    "story_icon": "",
    "outline": {
        "title": [
            "剧情概要"
        ],
        "content": [
            "奈文追上了少年并问他为何鲁莽行事。\\n原来少年的母亲是炼狱之匙的主人。\\n与此同时，与伊莉雅一起行动的少年的母亲\\n也表明了自己炼狱之匙主人的身份，\\n并决定解除炼狱文书的封印。"
        ]
    },
    "story_content": [
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120017_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "阿尔夫",
            "context": "啊！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22903_03_0001",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120017_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "阿尔夫",
            "context": "呜、呜哇啊啊啊啊！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22903_03_0002",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110365_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈文",
            "context": "还好赶上了！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22903_03_0003",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210132_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "拉米艾尔",
            "context": "你没受伤吧？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22903_03_0004",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120017_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "阿尔夫",
            "context": "……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22903_03_0005",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120017_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈文",
            "context": "等等！你还想被魔兽袭击吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22903_03_0006",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120017_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "阿尔夫",
            "context": "放开我！你们是坏人！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22903_03_0007",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210132_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "拉米艾尔",
            "context": "坏人？什么意思？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22903_03_0008",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120017_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "阿尔夫",
            "context": "你们在找炼狱之匙对吧！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22903_03_0009",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210132_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "拉米艾尔",
            "context": "你听到我们说话了啊。\\n不过，你为什么会知道炼狱之匙……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22903_03_0010",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210132_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "拉米艾尔",
            "context": "难道你就是炼狱之匙的主人？\\n你坚决不肯说自己的来历\\n也是因为这个？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22903_03_0011",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110365_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈文",
            "context": "不，不对。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22903_03_0012",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110365_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈文",
            "context": "炼狱之匙的主人不是阿尔夫，\\n而是他的父母。\\n而且还是养父母。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22903_03_0013",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110365_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈文",
            "context": "我没说错吧，阿尔夫。\\n你得知我们的目的后为了给父母报信，\\n才会不顾危险连夜跑向雪山。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22903_03_0014",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110365_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈文",
            "context": "如果你的父母是炼狱之匙的主人，\\n那就很容易理解你为什么\\n异常执着于血缘关系了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22903_03_0015",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210132_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "拉米艾尔",
            "context": "炼狱之匙只能通过血脉传承。\\n所以你才……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22903_03_0016",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120017_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "阿尔夫",
            "context": "我是不会告诉你们妈妈在哪里的！\\n要杀要剐随便你们！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22903_03_0017",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120017_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "阿尔夫",
            "context": "明知自己什么忙都帮不上……\\n又怎么可能再给她添麻烦。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22903_03_0018",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210132_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "拉米艾尔",
            "context": "这话是什么意思？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22903_03_0019",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120017_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "阿尔夫",
            "context": "我还以为只要我继承了炼狱之匙，\\n妈妈就能获得自由。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22903_03_0020",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120017_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "阿尔夫",
            "context": "可是，我是她捡来的孩子……\\n我没法让妈妈获得自由。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22903_03_0021",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120017_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "阿尔夫",
            "context": "我很爱妈妈，却什么也帮不上……\\n我、我……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22903_03_0022",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110365_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈文",
            "context": "阿尔夫……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22903_03_0023",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110365_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "SYS",
            "context": "与此同时，伊莉雅二人……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "有一帮北部教会的人\\n也混进这城镇里了。\\n他们的目的和我们一样。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22903_03_0024",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110369_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莫尔提斯",
            "context": "这样下去有可能会被他们\\n抢先一步夺走炼狱文书。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22903_03_0025",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110369_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莫尔提斯",
            "context": "你有什么对策吗，伊莉雅？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22903_03_0026",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "这个嘛，暂时还……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22903_03_0027",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "啊！咦？艾丽泽你不是\\n睡了吗？有什么事吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22903_03_0028",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120064_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "艾丽泽",
            "context": "你就是……伊莉雅大人对吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22903_03_0029",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "呃！？不、不是，我是艾莉雅，\\n不是伊莉雅……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22903_03_0030",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120064_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "艾丽泽",
            "context": "1000年前，有位少女\\n为了从灾难中拯救世界，\\n不惜以自己为活祭，投身异界。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22903_03_0031",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120064_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "艾丽泽",
            "context": "那位少女就是女神伊莉雅\\n养育的第一个女儿。\\n您就是那个少女，对吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22903_03_0032",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "你为什么会知道……难道……\\n你就是炼狱之匙的主人！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22903_03_0033",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120064_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "艾丽泽",
            "context": "正是。我是受女神伊莉雅之托\\n保管炼狱之匙的血统继承人。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22903_03_0034",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110369_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莫尔提斯",
            "context": "没想到我们要找的人就在身边。\\n真是太好了，伊莉雅。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22903_03_0035",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "是、是啊。不过我还有点混乱……\\n让我梳理一下情况。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22903_03_0036",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "首先，你住在这个镇上？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22903_03_0037",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120064_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "艾丽泽",
            "context": "我并不住在这里。\\n平日里我会在雪山上设下结界，\\n并在结界里生活。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22903_03_0038",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110369_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莫尔提斯",
            "context": "竟然能居住在雪山里。\\n看来是相当厉害的结界啊。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22903_03_0039",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120064_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "艾丽泽",
            "context": "据说我的祖先是侍奉\\n女神伊莉雅的大魔法师。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22903_03_0040",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120064_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "艾丽泽",
            "context": "也许是受此影响，\\n我们一族都比较擅长使用魔法。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22903_03_0041",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120064_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "艾丽泽",
            "context": "之所以能使用强大的结界魔法也是如此。\\n我们正是靠着这代代相传的结界魔法\\n才能将炼狱之匙守护至今。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22903_03_0042",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120064_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "艾丽泽",
            "context": "我们很少会外出。\\n一直在结界里过着\\n自给自足的隐居生活。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22903_03_0043",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "而你却不惜涉险在星龙祭之时\\n跑来这耳目众多的城镇。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22903_03_0044",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "你是真的在找你的儿子吧？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22903_03_0045",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120064_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "艾丽泽",
            "context": "每年只有这个时候我才会允许他\\n下山到城镇来。因为有必要让他\\n接触外界积累经验。可是……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22903_03_0046",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110369_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莫尔提斯",
            "context": "他却没有回去。\\n所以你才跑出结界来到镇上找人。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22903_03_0047",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120064_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "艾丽泽",
            "context": "既然还有其他人在寻找我，\\n那我就更担心了。\\n我的儿子也许会因此遭遇不测……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22903_03_0048",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "嗯，要尽快找到他才行。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22903_03_0049",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120064_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "艾丽泽",
            "context": "伊莉雅大人，\\n我有个不情之请。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22903_03_0050",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120064_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "艾丽泽",
            "context": "我现在就去森林的洞窟里，\\n用炼狱之匙打开异界，\\n取出炼狱文书。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22903_03_0051",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120064_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "艾丽泽",
            "context": "然后将炼狱文书交给你。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22903_03_0052",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "你确定要这么做吗……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22903_03_0053",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120064_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "艾丽泽",
            "context": "嗯。我所守护的这卷文书，\\n正是应当交给你来看的东西。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22903_03_0054",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120064_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "艾丽泽",
            "context": "作为交换……\\n我恳请你能帮我\\n寻找并保护我的儿子。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22903_03_0055",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110369_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莫尔提斯",
            "context": "就算你不说，我们也会这么做的。\\n你说是吧，伊莉雅？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22903_03_0056",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "嗯，即使没有交换条件\\n我们也会帮忙的。\\n这件事就交给我们吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22903_03_0057",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120064_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "艾丽泽",
            "context": "那我这就去森林\\n取出炼狱文书交给你。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22903_03_0058",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "夜路很危险，\\n我们陪你一起去吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22903_03_0059",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "梅奈……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22903_03_0060",
            "book_image": ""
        }
    ]
}